---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — MoniMata"
  description="MoniMata privacy policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  ogImage="/og/privacy-policy.png"
>
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-30 pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-200 mx-auto px-8">
      <h1 class="text-[48px] font-bold leading-[1.2] text-primary-dark mb-8">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: May 2026</p>

      <div
        class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-text-body leading-[1.7] space-y-6"
      >
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          1. Introduction
        </h2>
        <p>
          MoniMata ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your
          privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose,
          and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application and
          website (collectively, the "Service").
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          2. Information We Collect
        </h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-text-heading mt-6 mb-3">
          Personal Information
        </h3>
        <p>When you create an account, we may collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Name and email address</li>
          <li>Phone number</li>
          <li>Date of birth</li>
          <li>Educational institution (optional)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-text-heading mt-6 mb-3">
          Financial Information
        </h3>
        <p>To provide our budgeting services, we may collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Income information you manually provide</li>
          <li>Spending categories and amounts you log</li>
          <li>Savings goals you set</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We do <strong>not</strong> collect bank account numbers, passwords, or credit/debit
          card details. MoniMata is a budgeting and tracking tool, not a payment processor.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-text-heading mt-6 mb-3">
          Usage Data
        </h3>
        <p>
          We automatically collect certain information about your device and
          usage, including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Device type and operating system</li>
          <li>App usage patterns and feature interactions</li>
          <li>Crash reports and performance data</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          3. How We Use Your Information
        </h2>
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide and maintain the Service</li>
          <li>Personalize your budgeting experience</li>
          <li>Send smart nudges and spending alerts</li>
          <li>Power gamification features (points, badges, leaderboards)</li>
          <li>Improve our app and develop new features</li>
          <li>Communicate important updates and announcements</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          4. Data Sharing
        </h2>
        <p>
          We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal information. We may share
          data only with:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>
            Service providers who assist in operating the app (hosting,
            analytics)
          </li>
          <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          5. Data Security
        </h2>
        <p>
          We implement industry-standard security measures including encryption
          in transit and at rest, secure authentication, and regular security
          audits. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          6. Your Rights
        </h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Access and download your data</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Delete your account and associated data</li>
          <li>Opt out of non-essential communications</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          7. Children's Privacy
        </h2>
        <p>
          MoniMata is designed for users aged 16 and above. We do not knowingly
          collect information from children under 16.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          8. Changes to This Policy
        </h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify
          you of any material changes through the app or via email.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-text-heading mt-10 mb-4">
          9. Contact Us
        </h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at:</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> privacy@monimata.ng</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
